# Audit Log

This file logs all potentially sensitive operations for security review.

Format: JSON Lines (one JSON object per line)

Fields:
- timestamp: ISO-8601 timestamp with timezone
- session: session identifier
- user: user identifier
- channel: channel/DM identifier  
- action: operation type (exec, read, write, message, etc.)
- target: target of the operation (file path, command, etc.)
- status: allowed / blocked / error
- reason: why it was allowed or blocked

